<html>

<head>
<META NAME="ROBOTS" CONTENT="NOINDEX, NOFOLLOW">
<META NAME="ROBOTS" CONTENT="NOARCHIVE">

<title>Movers Arena</title>
<STYLE TYPE="text/css">
 	A:hover		{	text-decoration: nounderline;
 					color: red}
 	A			{	text-decoration: underline;
					color: blue}
</STYLE>
</head>
<body>
<div align="center">
  <center>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" width="700" height="13">
  <tr>
    <td width="100%" height="13" bgcolor="#FFCF63">
    &nbsp;</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="100%" bgcolor="#4A698C" height="37" align="center"><b>
    <font face="Verdana" size="4" color="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;Movers Arena</font></b></td>
  </tr>
</table>
  </center>
</div>
<div align="center">
  <center>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" width="700" height="22">
  <tr>
    <td class="NAVOFF" width="700" bgcolor="#CECFCE" align="center" height="22">
    <b><font face="Verdana" size="2">Your Fine Source for Online Moving Estimates </font></b></td>
  </tr>
</table>
  </center>
</div>
<div align="center">
  <center>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" width="700" height="1">
  <tr>
    <td width="23" bgcolor="#CECFCE" height="19">&nbsp;</td>
    <td width="677" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" height="19">
    <b>
    <font face="Verdana" color="#CE0000" size="2">&nbsp;Welcome <%=ALLT(pcCOMPANY)%></font></b></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="23" bgcolor="#CECFCE" height="19">&nbsp;</td>
    <td width="677" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" height="5">
    <hr color="#000000" width="694" size="0"></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="23" bgcolor="#CECFCE" height="56">&nbsp;</td>
    <td width="677" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" height="56">

     <!-- Body 1 Starts -->

<!--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->     

 	  	  
     <b><font face="Verdana" size="2">&nbsp;Thank you for selecting Movers Arena as your source for quality moving estimates.</font></b><p>
     <b><font face="Verdana" size="2">&nbsp;Please  follow the steps in order to use the system :</font></b></p>
     <ul>
       <li><b><font face="Verdana"><font size="2">Click on the link  to access your secured personal account:<br>
       </font>
       <a href="http://www.moversarena.com/<%=ALLT(pcCUSTNO)%>/admin.htm" target="_blank">
       <font size="2">http://www.moversarena.com/<%=ALLT(pcCUSTNO)%>/admin.htm</font></a><font size="2"><br>
       &nbsp;</font></font></b></li>
       <li><font face="Verdana"><b><font size="2">The username and the 
       password were randomly selected by the system and&nbsp; they are not to 
       be shared with anyone. <br>
       Username: <font color="#CE0000">online</font><br>
       Password: <font color="#CE0000">estimates</font><br>
&nbsp;</font></b></font></li>
       <li><font face="Verdana"><b><font size="2">The system has created&nbsp; 
       personal username and&nbsp; password for entering the system.<br>
       Username: <font color="#CE0000"><%=ALLT(lower(pcUSERNAME))%></font><br>
       Password: <font color="#CE0000"><%=ALLT(lower(pcCUSTNO))%></font></b></li>
     </ul>
     <p><font face="Verdana" size="2"><b>&nbsp;To purchase estimates, click on 
     Online Estimates at the Main Menu. <br>
     &nbsp;For further information and customer support email us at
     <a href="mailto:estimates@moversarena.com">estimates@moversarena.com</a>.</b></font></p>
     <p><b><font face="Verdana" size="2">&nbsp;Thanks again,</font></b></p>
     <p><b><font face="Verdana" size="2">&nbsp;Movers Arena.</font></b></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="23" bgcolor="#CECFCE" height="19">&nbsp;</td>
    <td width="677" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" height="1">&nbsp;</td>
  </tr>
  </table>


<!--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->     


	<!-- Body 1 Ends -->  

<TABLE CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="0" WIDTH="700" BORDER="0"> 
  <TR> 
	<TD BGCOLOR="#CECFCE" HEIGHT="5">
    <b><font face="Verdana" size="2">
    <IMG HEIGHT="1" ALT="" SRC="../spacer.htm" WIDTH="1" BORDER="0"></font></b></TD>
	</TR>
</TABLE> 
  </center>
</div>

<hr color="#000000" width="700">

</body>

</html>